signatures.p:
Leaf signatures (mostly cropped) consisting of combinations of letters (Quire 1: 'A';
                                            Quire 2: 'B'; Quire 3: 'C'; Quire 4: 'D'; Quire 5: '[E]'; Quire 6: 'ff'; Quire 7: '[G]'; Quire 8: '[H]';
                                            Quire 9: 'J'; Quire 10: 'K') with Roman numerals.
